    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Spirit)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Genjutsu Kai. The bonus to the dispel check is up to +15.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step increases the maximum bonus to the dispel check by +2. The fifth step allows you to pay double the cost to make two dispel checks, either against the same effect or two separate ones. Obtaining mastery requires you to be ECL 8 for the first step, +2 for each additional step.</p>\n",
